## Pre-Commit Checks

The following are hard violations that block commits:
- [ ] No cross-segment internal imports (see Forbidden Imports)
- [ ] No I/O packages in pure-logic segments
- [ ] No type definitions wrapping or extending schema types outside schema segments
- [ ] No circular dependencies between segments
- [ ] No mutable state outside declared state types in stateful segments
